===Etymology===
From {{inh|es|osp|huesso}}, from {{inh|es|la|ossum}}, popular variant of {{m|la|os}}, ''ossis'', ultimately from {{inh|es|ine-pro|*h₃ésth₁||bone}}, {{m|ine-pro|*h₂óst}}. Compare Catalan ''[[os]]'', French ''[[os]]'', Interlingua ''[[osso]]'', Italian ''[[osso]]'', Portuguese ''[[osso]]'', Romanian ''[[os]]'', Sardinian ''[[ossu]]''.
Political sense comes from comparing a dog looking for and defending a bone and a politician searching a position.

